name: gpt1-take-home-puppy
description: You can't resist the cute face of the puppy and decide to buy it. You take the puppy home and give it a warm and loving welcome. What's the first thing you do with your new furry friend?

name: gpt1-give-up-home
description: Feeling disheartened, you decide to give up on finding another animal and head back home. As you enter your empty house, you can't help but feel a sense of loneliness. What do you do to lift your spirits?

options.description: Call a friend and share your feelings
